<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Balthasar von Murach zu Flügelsberg und Wilhelm Groß zu Altenburg</head><p>Der Rat kündigt erneut Ulrich Schmid, Diener der Stadt, mit einem offenen Brief wegen der beschlagnahmten Schafe des Heinrich Rummel, Bürger zu Nürnberg, nach Vorgabe von Wilhelm von Wolfstein an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l31">Balthaſar <expan>Murach<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu <expan>flugelſp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l32">vnd <expan>wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> <expan>Groſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu der Altenbürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_148_r1l33"><expan>Lıeb<ex>er</ex></expan> Balthaſar vnd <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> / Als wir euch vormals <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_line_1575537002034_595">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1576744880064_4217">vnd den <expan>vlr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Smid </ab><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1576744883178_4222"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> cʒu euch </ab><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1576744885914_4227">geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab></add> von <expan>heincʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vnd <expan>Chuncʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> der Rumell <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l38"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / Alſo ſenden vvir aber cʒu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>denſ<ex>elben</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l40">vnd darcʒu auch ein abſchrift hẏrinne <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſʒe<ex>n</ex></expan> vvie </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l41">vns <expan>wılh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von wolfſtein / von der 
<del rend="strikethrough">S <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan></del> Schaf <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l43">dıe <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_148_line_1575537161064_615"><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Rumel <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> </ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan></del> <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan> ſein <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan> / <expan>geſ<ex>chriben</ex></expan> hat / Als vvir euch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l44">des vormals auch ein abſchrıfft in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brief <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſloſſen</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l45">geſant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / vvaʒ der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_148_r1l46">cʒu dıſem mal / an euch werb etc ut </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_148" id="72v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Balthasar <expan>Murach<ex>er</ex></expan> czu
                            <expan>Flugelsp<ex>er</ex>g</expan> und <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>
<expan>Grosze<ex>n</ex></expan> czu der Altenbürg </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Lieb<ex>er</ex></expan> Balthasar und
                        <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan>, als wir euch vormals
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
<add>und den <expan>Ulr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Smid,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, czu euch gesant
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan></add> von
                            <expan>Heincze<ex>n</ex></expan> und <expan>Chuncze<ex>n</ex></expan>,
                        der Rumell, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>. Also senden
                        wir aber czu <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> und darczu auch ein abschrift hyrinne
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slosze<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie uns
                                <expan>Wilh<ex>elm</ex></expan> von Wolfstein von der schaf
                                <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, die <expan>de<ex>m</ex></expan>
<add><expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Rumel, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan></add>, <expan>genome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        sein <expan>worde<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ges<ex>chriben</ex></expan> hat, als wir euch des vormals auch ein
                        abschrifft in <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> brief
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>slossen</expan> gesant <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                        Und <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, waz der
                            <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan>, <expan>dar<ex>umb</ex></expan> czu disem mal
                        an euch werb etc. ut<app><note>Text bricht hier ab. Vermutlich fehlt "supra".</note></app> </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
